@node towlower
@section @code{towlower}---translate wide characters to lowercase
@findex towlower
@strong{Synopsis}
@example
#include <wctype.h>
wint_t towlower(wint_t @var{c});

@end example
@strong{Description}@*
@code{towlower} is a function which converts uppercase wide characters to
lowercase, leaving all other characters unchanged.

@*
@strong{Returns}@*
@code{towlower} returns the lowercase equivalent of @var{c} when it is a
uppercase wide character; otherwise, it returns the input character.

@*
@strong{Portability}@*
@code{towlower} is C99.

No supporting OS subroutines are required.

@*
